Package: imagery.oregonexplorer.info
Title: Oregon Imagery Explorer Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Oregon Imagery Explorer ArcGIS server. Lists aerial imagery services (NAIP, OSIP) and retrieves service metadata including spatial extent, resolution, and band information.
